    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113370/extras/e4a230f2f4303019aa6e9e16f8e3c710.avif?t=1663018150\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful minimalist design and a relaxing atmosphere</h2><br>Hex Picross was assembled with a beautiful and relaxing minimalist design<br>Made with relaxing visual and sound effects<br>In addition to music prepared exclusively<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113370/extras/7226b9ffa946db19d8cbd352a2cb7dd9.poster.avif?t=1663018150\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113370/extras/7226b9ffa946db19d8cbd352a2cb7dd9.webm?t=1663018150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113370/extras/7226b9ffa946db19d8cbd352a2cb7dd9.mp4?t=1663018150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You need to click on the hexagonal cells to make them colored<br>Each diagonal and column counts how many colored cells there are<br>Your challenge is to find all the intersections between columns and diagonals<br>With this, they will decrease their number and will be equal to zero.<br>When all are equal to zero, you've won the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Many Difficulty  Levels</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3x3x3 - 40 Levels<br></li><li>4x4x4 - 40 Levels<br></li><li>5x5x5 - 40 Levels<br></li><li>6x6x6 - 40 Levels<br></li><li>7x7x7- 40 Levels<br></li><li>9x9x9 - 40 Levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Resources</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalist: no timer and no pressure, solve puzzles in your own time<br></li><li>Premium: 240 carefully chosen levels<br></li><li>Zen: Zen and relaxing sound environment<br></li><li>Dark Mode: Perfect if you can't stare at the white screen for too long<br></li><li>Steam Cloud and Steam Achivements</li></ul>",
